- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses techniques supporting preference articulation and dynamic problems, which are common topics in AI research. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possible category as the paper mentions support for parallel computing in multicore and cluster systems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the availability of libraries for data processing, data analysis, and data visualization, which are commonly used in machine learning. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper describes the development of a software platform for multi-objective optimization.
